01:44:47.959 --> 01:44:50.875
Please! Father! Father!

01:44:50.875 --> 01:44:52.500
Take care of the kids!

01:45:08.292 --> 01:45:11.459
I see that you're not afraid to die.

01:45:11.667 --> 01:45:14.334
Life and death are one.

01:45:14.834 --> 01:45:17.750
How could I be afraid?

01:45:17.959 --> 01:45:20.375
The compassion of Buddha.

01:45:20.542 --> 01:45:24.875
Let's see how much of that you truly believe.

01:45:29.209 --> 01:45:31.792
Where is your base of operations?

01:45:36.750 --> 01:45:38.209
What are you doing?

01:45:38.209 --> 01:45:42.167
