01:46:22.125 --> 01:46:24.334
Lower your sword!

01:46:24.709 --> 01:46:29.334
The power you cannot control will only harm you!

01:46:29.417 --> 01:46:31.250
Lower your sword!

01:46:33.000 --> 01:46:34.417
Stop it!

01:46:35.167 --> 01:46:38.042
Stop! Enough!

01:46:39.292 --> 01:46:44.250
I will not forgive you, even in death!

01:46:45.750 --> 01:46:49.084
Mercy and forgiveness are Buddhist values.

01:46:51.959 --> 01:46:55.792
You are far from reaching enlightenment.

01:47:58.542 --> 01:47:59.667
You're back!

01:47:59.667 --> 01:48:01.709
Your late father always said,

01:48:02.000 --> 01:48:04.042
'know your place in life.'

01:48:04.875 --> 01:48:09.125
We cannot survive just by being good.

01:48:19.500 --> 01:48:22.417
- Dochi!
- Brother!

01:48:33.667 --> 01:48:36.000
