01:49:02.500 --> 01:49:03.875
Dae-nam!

01:50:01.542 --> 01:50:03.500
Open your eyes!

01:50:13.125 --> 01:50:14.917
Find the bald bandit.

01:50:35.042 --> 01:50:37.000
You sons of bitches!

01:50:47.917 --> 01:50:49.625
Get inside.

01:50:49.709 --> 01:50:51.375
