01:58:00.042 --> 01:58:01.917
Please give him to me.

01:58:03.584 --> 01:58:05.459
Don't you dare come near!

01:58:06.875 --> 01:58:08.625
Please lower your sword.

01:58:08.834 --> 01:58:14.792
Come any closer, and I'll slice you open!

01:58:27.667 --> 01:58:30.167
No better than a beast!

01:58:30.417 --> 01:58:33.000
Even as a concubine's son,

01:58:33.334 --> 01:58:37.625
