Here is your sentence!

02:00:33.292 --> 02:00:36.417
The Mt. Jiri bandits' crimes are as follows:

02:00:36.959 --> 02:00:42.959
First, larceny and the murder of noblemen.

02:00:43.250 --> 02:00:49.292
