02:02:44.875 --> 02:02:47.917
You sons of bitches!

02:03:24.917 --> 02:03:26.542
Let go of me!

02:03:34.084 --> 02:03:35.709
How dare you!

02:03:42.250 --> 02:03:44.584
You'll be punished!

02:03:48.792 --> 02:03:50.084
Move, move!

02:03:50.084 --> 02:03:51.417
Just hold on!

02:03:54.417 --> 02:03:56.375
Are you okay? Let me see you.

02:03:58.459 --> 02:03:59.875
